description.narrative:
The final objective is to produce a project document which will be formulated and developed jointly by INSD and Statistics Sweden.
Specifically, the contribution aims to:
1) Identify the appropriate form of cooperation taking into account past experiences and the local context;
2) Make a technical and financial analysis allowing the implementation of the project according to the GAR methodology;
3) Specify the decision-making process for the implementation of the project.
